            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Intraduisible.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Not usefully translatable</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Intraducibile.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p>غير قابل للترجمة بشكل جيد</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>The vestige of letter before omicron might be the upper part of a iota but also of other letters.</p>
	   <p>The style of lettering and layout is quite similar with <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr012400</ref> and <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr012700</ref>, hence the proposed date.</p>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
